"1  (9-lb.) reduced-sodium, bone-in cured ham","1  (750-milliliter) bottle extra-dry Champagne or other dry sparkling white wine, divided","2 cups packed light brown sugar, divided","1/4 cup pure maple syrup or honey","1/4 cup canned crushed pineapple in juice","2 tablespoons Dijon mustard","1/2 teaspoon ground cloves","  Pineapple slices (optional)"